name: Cellenza Wonder Sealer Pro
description: Cellenza Wonder Sealer Pro is the Premium densification that makes the marble harder and denser. Wonder penetrates into the marble and reacts with the marble to form compounds which expand and fill the pores in the stone. Not only does this reduce the porosity but also leads to enhanced shine and longevity of polish.
